### Health check
GET http://localhost:8000/health
Accept: application/json

### Trigger ingestion (local sample)
POST http://localhost:8000/ingest
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "full_refresh": false,
  "paths": []
}

### Ask a question
POST http://localhost:8000/ask
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "question": "What is the rated print speed of the AC7070?",
  "session_id": "local-dev",
  "filters": {}
}

### Run evaluation suite
POST http://localhost:8000/eval/run
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "output_dir": "eval/runs/manual"
}

### Admin dictionary (GET)
GET http://localhost:8000/admin/dictionary
Accept: application/json

### Admin dictionary (POST)
POST http://localhost:8000/admin/dictionary
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "entries": [
    {"term": "ADF", "synonyms": ["automatic document feeder"]}
  ]
}

### Admin session logs (HTML)
GET http://localhost:8000/admin/sessions?format=html
Accept: text/html
